Pandemia author Alex Berenson brings us the covid data they’re hiding from us, talks about how everyone now knows what he's been saying for two years is right, weighs in on the bogus NYT story on lab leak theory. California, Washington and Oregon drop school mask mandates. Why is Biden still wearing a mask outside? Biden regime advising wearing masks in nuclear fallout bunker. ABC's Jon Karl on coming GOP election wave. SNL skit suggests mask, vax mandates may have been wrong.
